00:35:15.550 --> 00:35:18.640 align:middle line:90%
So this is not necessary.

00:35:18.640 --> 00:35:21.340 align:middle line:90%
>> Does the compound evaporate?

00:35:21.340 --> 00:35:23.770 align:middle line:90%
Is it absorbed into food?

00:35:23.770 --> 00:35:27.490 align:middle line:84%
Scientists are investigating
these unanswered questions,

00:35:27.490 --> 00:35:30.100 align:middle line:84%
