conduct our investigation.

00:35:55.580 --> 00:35:59.410 align:middle line:84%
So one day, I found myself
in deepest West Virginia,

00:35:59.410 --> 00:36:02.620 align:middle line:84%
following the tracks of
perfluorated compounds

00:36:02.620 --> 00:36:06.260 align:middle line:84%
in Paul Brooks's
