00:38:42.190 --> 00:38:43.660 align:middle line:90%
often at a high dose.

00:38:43.660 --> 00:38:54.506 align:middle line:90%


00:38:54.506 --> 00:39:06.810 align:middle line:84%
>> So I take probably, let's
