00:39:06.810 --> 00:39:10.825 align:middle line:90%
12, 13, 14, 15, 16.

00:39:10.825 --> 00:39:11.625 align:middle line:90%
16.

00:39:11.625 --> 00:39:15.040 align:middle line:90%


00:39:15.040 --> 00:39:20.050 align:middle line:84%
