00:40:36.880 --> 00:40:40.480 align:middle line:90%


00:40:40.480 --> 00:40:43.590 align:middle line:84%
The DuPont trial started
to make the headlines,

00:40:43.590 --> 00:40:47.540 align:middle line:84%
