kilometers away from them.

00:40:47.540 --> 00:40:49.850 align:middle line:90%
It was so far away.

00:40:49.850 --> 00:40:50.750 align:middle line:90%
It couldn't be that.

00:40:50.750 --> 00:40:54.080 align:middle line:90%


00:40:54.080 --> 00:40:59.660 align:middle line:84%
Until 2005, when the
couple received a letter.

00:40:59.660 --> 00:41:02.690 align:middle line:84%
>> They came out with saying
I don't know exactly how many

00:41:02.690 --> 00:41:05.840 align:middle line:84%
