would come out of it,

00:41:21.190 --> 00:41:25.810 align:middle line:84%
but anyway, so we went
through the first testing

00:41:25.810 --> 00:41:26.785 align:middle line:90%
and the second testing.

00:41:26.785 --> 00:41:30.160 align:middle line:90%


00:41:30.160 --> 00:41:34.120 align:middle line:84%
>> Gwen and Earl had in fact
joined a study of 70,000

00:41:34.120 --> 00:41:37.690 align:middle line:90%
inhabitants in the region.

00:41:37.690 --> 00:41:42.310 align:middle line:84%
The largest scientific study
on the effect of PFOA on humans

00:41:42.310 --> 00:41:45.340 align:middle line:84%
was conducted by
three epidemiologists

00:41:45.340 --> 00:41:48.370 align:middle line:84%
from reputable English
and American universities.

00:41:48.370 --> 00:41:55.000 align:middle line:90%


00:41:55.000 --> 00:41:58.690 align:middle line:84%
In 2012, David Savitz
and his colleagues

00:41:58.690 --> 00:42:00.400 align:middle line:90%
published their results.

00:42:00.400 --> 00:42:04.390 align:middle line:90%
They were unequivocal.

00:42:04.390 --> 00:42:09.370 align:middle line:84%
