exposure and a health problem.

00:42:23.860 --> 00:42:29.110 align:middle line:84%
And those included heart
disease, the various forms.

00:42:29.110 --> 00:42:30.910 align:middle line:84%
We weren't able to
be more specific,

00:42:30.910 --> 00:42:33.340 align:middle line:84%
but various forms
of heart disease.

00:42:33.340 --> 00:42:41.540 align:middle line:84%
Kidney cancer, testicular
cancer, thyroid disease,

00:42:41.540 --> 00:42:46.240 align:middle line:84%
ulcerative colitis, a
disease of the intestines,

00:42:46.240 --> 00:42:50.290 align:middle line:84%
