00:45:18.490 --> 00:45:22.660 align:middle line:84%
which needed the precious
input of industrialists, DuPont

00:45:22.660 --> 00:45:25.890 align:middle line:90%
and their PFC-based Teflon.

00:45:25.890 --> 00:45:30.510 align:middle line:84%
