00:45:30.510 --> 00:45:32.790 align:middle line:90%
atomic bomb.

00:45:32.790 --> 00:45:36.660 align:middle line:84%
Giant, huge
quantities of fluoride

00:45:36.660 --> 00:45:43.810 align:middle line:84%
