influence was Teflon.

00:46:10.950 --> 00:46:12.900 align:middle line:84%
Teflon was something
that DuPont had

00:46:12.900 --> 00:46:14.980 align:middle line:90%
an expertise in manufacturing.

00:46:14.980 --> 00:46:17.340 align:middle line:84%
So DuPont's
expertise in fluoride

00:46:17.340 --> 00:46:22.440 align:middle line:84%
was really the secret weapon
