know her levels of PFC,

00:52:41.810 --> 00:52:45.120 align:middle line:84%
because she is a scientist
and was working on a study

00:52:45.120 --> 00:52:47.070 align:middle line:90%
on the subject.

00:52:47.070 --> 00:52:50.850 align:middle line:84%
We could all have this
test, but it is expensive,

00:52:50.850 --> 00:52:55.770 align:middle line:84%
because it is only conducted
in specialized laboratories.

00:52:55.770 --> 00:52:58.590 align:middle line:84%
Jonrit Halling was not
surprised to discover

00:52:58.590 --> 00:53:03.240 align:middle line:84%
that she was contaminated,
probably alongside all mothers

00:53:03.240 --> 00:53:05.040 align:middle line:90%
on the planet.

00:53:05.040 --> 00:53:08.340 align:middle line:84%
Since then, PFCs have
put into question

00:53:08.340 --> 00:53:11.790 align:middle line:90%
the benefits of breastfeeding.

00:53:11.790 --> 00:53:15.420 align:middle line:84%
>> I think it's a shame, because
of course breastfeeding is

00:53:15.420 --> 00:53:19.200 align:middle line:84%
the most natural thing,
and it is still, I think,

00:53:19.200 --> 00:53:21.310 align:middle line:90%
the best for your baby.

00:53:21.310 --> 00:53:24.510 align:middle line:84%
And as an individual,
it's very hard

00:53:24.510 --> 00:53:27.670 align:middle line:84%
to do anything to
avoid this exposure.

00:53:27.670 --> 00:53:32.340 align:middle line:84%
And also, if you buy clothes
and shoes for children,

00:53:32.340 --> 00:53:34.770 align:middle line:90%
it's very difficult to avoid.

00:53:34.770 --> 00:53:36.990 align:middle line:84%
>> Difficult, but
not impossible.

00:53:36.990 --> 00:53:42.200 align:middle line:90%


00:53:42.200 --> 00:53:47.180 align:middle line:84%
