00:55:31.740 --> 00:55:34.920 align:middle line:84%
PFC material, so we could
compare the functionality

00:55:34.920 --> 00:55:36.307 align:middle line:90%
in the same conditions.

00:55:36.307 --> 00:55:38.640 align:middle line:84%
And we've asked our-- we had
our athletes wear those out

00:55:38.640 --> 00:55:45.060 align:middle line:84%
