00:57:16.060 --> 00:57:20.630 align:middle line:90%


00:57:20.630 --> 00:57:23.810 align:middle line:84%
There is still a long but
necessary battle ahead

00:57:23.810 --> 00:57:27.920 align:middle line:84%
to rid the planet of this
authorized toxic companion.

